As a Rajasthani it is said that our parents stop to communicate in Rajasthani.😢 Rajasthani language ki history 1000 saal se hai hamare folk hamare cloth me Aaj bhi jinda hai but in schools teachers punish us when we speak in Rajasthani and tell us to speak Hindi and English in schools.
Our govt.and people are not serious towards Rajasthani languages.Hindi and English languages replace Rajasthani language ..This is serious issue hope people of Rajasthan understand it...
